{
  "stem": "20218.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When I came home, my mother came tired and brought a little from potato skins-- the potato skins, really, so she could make something for us to eat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "My father was still working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my brother was hungry, and the piece of bread, what we got for the ration-- many times, he ate it, not left-- not leaving anything for me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But there were-- they were kids.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I, I probably was angry, but I don't remember too much about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Then one day we were-- we were there for four and a half years in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Somehow, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We had to blow on the stove to, to, to warm up a little food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had the rations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then we heard that our, our elders, who was-- who the German took for him to manage the ghetto, he had an order to bring around, I don't know, 50 or more little children so they can send them out.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The whole population in the ghetto was so-- was so tragic, sad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Children, they took it away from their mothers, and they send them out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Nobody know where.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was really tragic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every day, a lot of people died from hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't manage.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't stay alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It was-- was 19-- I think it was 1943 or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said that we all have to leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We asked plenty, where we going to go?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody came back to tell us where they went.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One by one, they selected streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They selected people, and they took them away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother were taken away from home with other young men.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
